## plg_system_schema
- [x] Create a schema form in article edit view
- [x] Add 'Schema Type' list form field with 'None' selected by default

## plg_schemaorg_xxx
- [x] Create a new option in existing "Schema Type" list field in Schema form
- [x] Show form fields of selected schema type
- [x] Update type of form fields in schema form
- [x] Store form data in JSON format
- [x] Save into database
- [x] Fetch schema data from database and inject schema in head tag
